11:06.000Z","msg":"最大問題個KB阻住左，搞到個MON得四寸幾。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出返推機咪好LOR"},{"pid":"6b9ce8f608c8c7cf8822b37b58c58ac4cd2010fa","tid":565504,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T08:42:10.000Z","msg":"如果而家先打算買佢最新型號，貪佢夠安全嘅話，不如算數吧！<br />\nPriv係最後一部blackberry自己做嘅型號，之後嘅classic係富士康代工，再之後嘅dtek50/60到而家嘅keyone（無論係銀/黑/銅（即將推出））都好，世界版都係中國TCL代工，除非你有辦法買法印尼版（印尼製造），否則同買支那機冇分別。<br />\n仲有就係，而家用緊bb10 os 嘅，有得用就好好珍惜，因為一年後blackberry就唔再支援bb10 os 。<br />\nSource<br />\n<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2017/12/blackberry-os-end-2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2017%2F12%2Fblackberry-os-end-2019&d=NOwHBB%2FopAcSV4JlwH5Fel0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=374259f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/2017/12/blackberry-os-end-2019</a>"},{"pid":"80ab3f942916281e640ebbb7b1e24c683d4cca90","tid":565504,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a09989663dda5f914d4bb49bd79ab64eb2c06968","tid":565504,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T08:11:06.000Z","msg":"最大問題個KB阻住左，搞到個MON得四寸幾。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出返推機咪好LOR"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T08:45:28.000Z","msg":"可一不可再。<br />\n一來實體鍵盤冇乜市場，二來keyone係最後一部blackberry監督嘅手機，跟著就係由tcl 做，自己就搞軟件業務。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b05d976aec6475f3f4d386e7774223569325e98","tid":565504,"uid":164092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d0fb805c8f54624bded1ba102078976ee8b8385","tid":565504,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T04:50:55.000Z","msg":"想轉用，有無意見？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T09:30:04.000Z","msg":"你本來用緊咩機?"},{"pid":"ca406bd48d7422e521d5c43d4d46f1b44c810997","tid":565504,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b05d976aec6475f3f4d386e7774223569325e98","tid":565504,"uid":164092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"qu